Have you been working all night?

03:03.167 --> 03:04.666
Don't bother, she can't hear you.

03:04.668 --> 03:05.834
She's in a zone.

03:05.836 --> 03:07.469
Here, watch this.

03:07.471 --> 03:09.438
That's not really a
birthmark on your leg...

03:09.440 --> 03:11.606
I dropped a cigarette in your crib.

03:11.608 --> 03:13.375
See?

03:13.377 --> 03:16.511
I mean, I'm telling her stuff
I was saving for my deathbed.

